{"tid":1492273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"另類烈士勇武 中國律師維護法治","createTime":"2019-08-20T18:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T19:01:37.000Z","uid":58984,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"555d8bdb9c38bcb62bbc065f05a92e637c4ace47","tid":1492273,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:11:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/257416524693131/posts/739988423102603?s=100000743997688&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F257416524693131%2Fposts%2F739988423102603%3Fs%3D100000743997688%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41JggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=c34c3f10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/257416524693131/posts/739988423102603?s=100000743997688&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n早幾日喺連登開PO同大家講<br />\n有個大陸玩命律師8月18日監察香港情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109140177111638/posts/113341446691511?s=100000743997688&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109140177111638%2Fposts%2F113341446691511%3Fs%3D100000743997688%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41JggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=aa9b7f86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109140177111638/posts/113341446691511?s=100000743997688&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n結果今日講遺言 比大陸叫返內地<br />\n片入面都有暗示威脅佢身邊嘅人<br />\n而佢係為咗履行自己律師嘅責任<br />\n去守護自己所追求嘅法治精神<br />\n而睇得出佢不斷尋求自己嘅認同<br />\n話比自己知三年考個牌<br />\n今次做呢件事唔會後悔<br />\n<br />\n我目的唔係大和解<br />\n而係我想話比香港人知<br />\n一個唔係香港人都可以走到咁前<br />\n9&times;9返到大陸一定俾人關上洗腦設施<br />\n甚至俾人虐待等等 香港我哋都仲可以追究<br />\n大陸算啦佢返到上去死緊<br />\n<br />\n一個唔係生於香港嘅人都可以咁勇武<br />\n你地今日仲有啲咩藉口比自己停<br />\n依場運動開始咗就冇得返轉頭<br />\n希望大家勿忘初衷<br />\n老老實實至今犧牲嘅人已經好多<br />\n你有冇諗過其實人哋真係可能咁就一世㗎啦<br />\n佢哋無名咁犧牲都係為咗運動嘅成功<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家好好諗清楚咁多日發生嘅事情<br />\n經過8月18號其實大家都清楚件事就係民意唔會逆轉<br />\n大家希望好好諗清楚 好好下定決心對抗呢個政權<br />\n好好諗清楚點樣回應 為我地犧牲嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"16bcd691eaf4c01da8cbe6460d02f05df5635c8f","tid":1492273,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4704dc5105dc645c456371547933604bf48b3a52","tid":1492273,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a29fe5833afa87af189109c24e446a5fb4c8d9","tid":1492273,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"依家討論區俾人帶住風向走<br />\n真正有心post唔會有人覆<br />\n<br />\n如果獨立調查委員會話你知&quot;無高官需要問責&quot;你係咪要接受呀？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441577</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一接受成立獨立調查委員會，場運動就Total lost"},{"pid":"27bd462d3142107396442fb06d0a50d6c13d6091","tid":1492273,"uid":58984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b632d713150e88563853323a6395d44c1b90e3","tid":1492273,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c